      "content": "okay that makes sense. i'll try the small amounts. one more thing, i'm worried about the space behind the drywall itself. i've heard sometimes things can get weird behind the walls if the installation isn't tight, like if there are gaps or stuff trapped back there. does that actually matter for the finish?",
